description:
Non material minor admendment of planning permission ref P090206 dated 01 April 2009 for the 'Redevelopment of Regent Quarter Block D, comprising of part demolition, part conversion of existing buildings  and erection of part 2 to 6 storey buildings to accommodate 5439m² business (Use Class B1), 175m² restaurant (Use Class A3) and 54 residential units (19x1, 30x2 and 5x3 beds), with 135 cycle spaces, 3 disabled spaces and associated landscaping'. The non material admendments to 55 Balfe Street (former stable building) comprise of:
A] Insertion of double-height window within the north elevation (facing the internal courtyard);
B] Alteration to design of the entrance door from sliding door to side hung doors;
C] Change from flat to pitched roof over stair 2 to replicate existing condition;
D] Alteration to the gutter detail on pitched roof to replicate existing condition.
